primary.request: Register a new account on the website
primary.context: Caller received a message saying their ownership type requires special handling for registration
primary.detail: Agent verified the caller using contract ID and name, then sent a Clubhouse registration link via email.

steps: Caller requested help with website registration.
Agent attempted lookup by phone number but failed.
Agent successfully looked up record using Contract ID.
Agent verified caller's identity after initial name mismatch (caller provided parent's name).
Agent confirmed contact information on file.
Agent sent registration link to the email on file.

clarifications.note: Agent clarifying if registration or password reset
Agent asking for spelling of name

corrections.note: Caller explains multiple owners on contract after mismatch

actions.detail: Lookup by Brazilian phone number failed
First name provided did not match record
Verified using secondary owner name and state
Sent Clubhouse registration link to email

insights.summary: The caller wanted to register for the online portal but was blocked by a 'special handling' message. The agent successfully verified the account using a contract ID and sent the registration link to the email on file.
insights.verbatim: Perfect. So I have to log in in Vacatia, the new website.
